                    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Aliforenko (2025). Extracting Knowledge from Kubernetes Configuration Graphs. TScIT 43, University of Twente. Graph-based analysis; security section covers privileged containers, NetworkPolicy absence, and external exposure (LoadBalancer/NodePort/Ingress)."@en ;
                    rdfs:label "Aliforenko 2025"@en .


